VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT Intent\.get.*Extra\(".*"
WHEN EXPR PRESENT:(execute|query|rawQuery|execSQL|Runtime|ProcessBuilder|File\s*\(|URL\s*\(|startActivity|intent\.) && MISSING:(validate|sanitize|escape|encode|allowlist|whitelist)
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects the usage of Intent extras, which may contain untrusted inputs.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Untrusted Inputs: Intent Extras.
